(Kuan Lin is sleeping on the floor.)

788
00:33:57,823 --> 00:33:59,762
(Just a moment ago, )

789
00:33:59,763 --> 00:34:01,163
(things were good for us.)

790
00:34:02,033 --> 00:34:04,063
(You said that you missed me.)

791
00:34:04,263 --> 00:34:08,133
(Promise me that you won't forget about me.)

792
00:34:08,473 --> 00:34:09,943
I'll go and get him.

793
00:34:10,843 --> 00:34:12,343
The youngest one should go.

794
00:34:12,713 --> 00:34:14,112
(I'll go and get him.)

795
00:34:14,113 --> 00:34:15,682
Why is the sergeant going?

796
00:34:15,683 --> 00:34:16,683
Seriously.

797
00:34:16,813 --> 00:34:17,883
Sergeant.

798
00:34:17,943 --> 00:34:19,782
(Clueless, Dae Hwi lies back down.)

799
00:34:19,783 --> 00:34:22,753
You know, you should run when you're in the spotlight.

800
00:34:23,383 --> 00:34:25,522
- "You should run." - Hey, private.

801
00:34:25,523 --> 00:34:27,022
- He isn't running. - Me?

802
00:34:27,023 --> 00:34:28,092
(Oh, I'm a private.)

803
00:34:28,093 --> 00:34:30,322
I wanted to go and pick up my friend too.

804
00:34:30,323 --> 00:34:32,592
(He says those words, but lies back down.)

805
00:34:32,593 --> 00:34:34,462
When the orderly room asks for two soldiers...

806
00:34:34,463 --> 00:34:36,062
and you think you're included, you should go right away.

807
00:34:36,063 --> 00:34:37,102
Orderly room!

808
00:34:37,103 --> 00:34:39,003
Stop talking about the army!

809
00:34:39,073 --> 00:34:42,033
Don't exclude those who haven't served in the military.

810
00:34:42,403 --> 00:34:43,572
Once you join the military,

811
00:34:43,573 --> 00:34:46,412
you'll think, "The older members are incredible."

812
00:34:46,413 --> 00:34:48,272
- "How did they do this?" - I'll have my revenge...

813
00:34:48,273 --> 00:34:49,282
once I come back.

814
00:34:49,283 --> 00:34:51,642
- "How did they endure?" - Seriously.

815
00:34:51,643 --> 00:34:53,613
- Seriously. - I mean my words.

816
00:34:54,383 --> 00:34:56,082
(Sergeant Ong is back with Kuan Lin.)

817
00:34:56,083 --> 00:34:57,523
Kuan Lin, good night.

818
00:35:00,153 --> 00:35:01,322
- Seong Wu. - Make sure Kuan Lin is warm.

819
00:35:01,323 --> 00:35:02,522
Kuan Lin, good night.

820
00:35:02,523 --> 00:35:04,563
(Tucking Kuan Lin in)

821
00:35:04,923 --> 00:35:05,992
Good night.

822
00:35:05,993 --> 00:35:09,503
(Including Daniel and Kuan Lin, 11 members sleep together.)

823
00:35:11,233 --> 00:35:12,702
(Flapping)

824
00:35:12,703 --> 00:35:14,003
Did someone fart?

825
00:35:14,573 --> 00:35:16,443
(Wanna One Wants to Know)

826
00:35:17,843 --> 00:35:19,012
Who passed gas?

827
00:35:19,013 --> 00:35:20,533
(Case number 17-0807, Who Passed Gas?)

828
00:35:21,473 --> 00:35:23,043
(11 suspects)

829
00:35:24,883 --> 00:35:28,282
(At night, Mr. Park detects a suspicious smell.)

830
00:35:28,283 --> 00:35:29,652
- Hold on. - It's you, isn't it?

831
00:35:29,653 --> 00:35:31,422
(As he flaps the blanket, the smells grow stronger.)

832
00:35:31,423 --> 00:35:33,322
(Suspecting the others, he looks around.)

833
00:35:33,323 --> 00:35:34,392
(Laughing)

834
00:35:34,393 --> 00:35:35,522
It's you, isn't it?

835
00:35:35,523 --> 00:35:37,892
(He spots Mr. Kim laughing in a suspicious manner.)

836
00:35:37,893 --> 00:35:39,292
No.

837
00:35:39,293 --> 00:35:42,432
- Gosh, Kim Jae Hwan! - It isn't me.

838
00:35:42,433 --> 00:35:43,932
- Did you fart? - No, I didn't.

839
00:35:43,933 --> 00:35:45,362
- What? - Gosh, Kim Jae Hwan!

840
00:35:45,363 --> 00:35:47,033
I didn't fart, you punk!

841
00:35:47,603 --> 00:35:48,633
Did you fart?

842
00:35:49,073 --> 00:35:51,172
- When I brought it up, - No.

843
00:35:51,173 --> 00:35:52,812
- he was looking at me. - No.

844
00:35:52,813 --> 00:35:54,412
(The public opinion is unfavorable toward Mr. Kim.)

845
00:35:54,413 --> 00:35:55,413
Get out.

846
00:35:55,414 --> 00:35:57,242
- I didn't fart. - It doesn't smell here.

847
00:35:57,243 --> 00:35:58,982
("We swear it doesn't smell here.")

848
00:35:58,983 --> 00:36:00,382
- It doesn't smell here. - Seriously.

849
00:36:00,383 --> 00:36:03,082
(Backed by his witnesses, Mr. Kim pleads not guilty.)

850
00:36:03,083 --> 00:36:04,622
- Doesn't it smell? - Does it smell when I do this?

851
00:36:04,623 --> 00:36:06,223
- No, it doesn't. - It doesn't, right?

852
00:36:06,853 --> 00:36:08,922
(The public opinion wavers again.)

853
00:36:08,923 --> 00:36:09,923
(Sniffing)

854
00:36:09,924 --> 00:36:11,322
Woo Jin, did you open your mouth?

855
00:36:11,323 --> 00:36:12,562
("It began to stink because of Mr. Park's bad breath.")

856
00:36:12,563 --> 00:36:14,132
I opened my mouth, but...

857
00:36:14,133 --> 00:36:15,632
Had it been me, this side would've been smelly.

858
00:36:15,633 --> 00:36:17,113
- It doesn't smell here. - Seriously.

859
00:36:17,263 --> 00:36:19,072
(Insufficient evidence, prime suspect, alibi)

860
00:36:19,073 --> 00:36:21,372
(Wanna One Wants to Know awaits tip-offs from people...)

861
00:36:21,373 --> 00:36:23,903
(who are well-acquainted with Mr. Kim and Mr. Park.)

862
00:36:25,473 --> 00:36:26,573
- Guys. - Yes?

863
00:36:26,743 --> 00:36:30,342
This is our first night at Wanna Base.

864
00:36:30,343 --> 00:36:32,013
- It's a meaningful day. - That's right.

865
00:36:32,313 --> 00:36:33,583
I still can't believe it.

866
00:36:34,113 --> 00:36:35,313
At our last concert,

867
00:36:35,883 --> 00:36:38,482
I made a comment, "The one I won't be able..."

868
00:36:38,483 --> 00:36:40,723
"to call out for again, Wannable."

869
00:36:41,093 --> 00:36:43,322
The one I won't be able to call out for again,

870
00:36:43,323 --> 00:36:45,293
Wannable, I love you.

871
00:36:45,993 --> 00:36:49,733
But we're calling out for Wannable once again.

872
00:36:50,763 --> 00:36:53,033
It makes me go, "Is this for real?"

873
00:36:53,703 --> 00:36:55,632
I felt like too much time had passed.

874
00:36:55,633 --> 00:36:58,373
I'm so thankful that our fans have waited for us.

875
00:36:58,873 --> 00:37:02,173
I think Min Hyun was the one who said this at our last concert.

876
00:37:02,813 --> 00:37:05,952
"Wannable, please be happy even after Wanna One is gone."

877
00:37:05,953 --> 00:37:07,052
Min Hyun, was it you?

878
00:37:07,053 --> 00:37:08,983
Who made that comment?

879
00:37:09,583 --> 00:37:10,882
Someone did.

880
00:37:10,883 --> 00:37:12,083
(Everyone is deep in thought.)

881
00:37:12,253 --> 00:37:13,393
Was it Sang Gil?

882
00:37:13,453 --> 00:37:15,293
- Sang Gil? - What?

883
00:37:16,223 --> 00:37:17,522
Hold on a second.

884
00:37:17,523 --> 00:37:18,862
Imagine Sang Gil suddenly going,

885
00:37:18,863 --> 00:37:21,132
"Wannable, please be happy..."

886
00:37:21,133 --> 00:37:23,363
"even after Wanna One is gone."

887
00:37:24,133 --> 00:37:25,872
It's so funny.

888
00:37:25,873 --> 00:37:27,032
(Was Sang Gil the 13th star?)

889
00:37:27,033 --> 00:37:28,602
When you think about it, it's funny.

890
00:37:28,603 --> 00:37:30,572
- When you think about it... - Seriously.

891
00:37:30,573 --> 00:37:32,372
- Hey. - Think about it.

892
00:37:32,373 --> 00:37:34,449
(Wanna One is wide awake and the atmosphere is ruined.)

893
00:37:34,473 --> 00:37:36,713
(Stop laughing.)

894
00:37:37,043 --> 00:37:39,883
I feel like we've made it happen...

895
00:37:40,253 --> 00:37:41,913
years after the comment.

896
00:37:42,213 --> 00:37:44,922
Thinking about it makes us smile, right?

897
00:37:44,923 --> 00:37:45,952
(Wannable, please be happy.)

898
00:37:45,953 --> 00:37:47,522
(Thinking about it makes them laugh.)

899
00:37:47,523 --> 00:37:49,223
Was that why Sang Gil came?

900
00:37:49,493 --> 00:37:51,792
Did he come to pay back Wannable?

901
00:37:51,793 --> 00:37:53,463
Sang Gil was wearing makeup too.

902
00:37:54,693 --> 00:37:56,133
So funny.

903
00:37:57,463 --> 00:37:58,963
(Rolling on the floor)

904
00:37:59,173 --> 00:38:01,413
(Wanna One's laughter continues on deep into the night.)

905
00:38:02,543 --> 00:38:05,243
(Wanna One and Wannable, please be happy.)

906
00:38:06,613 --> 00:38:10,143
(And to Wanna One's 12th star)

907
00:38:10,743 --> 00:38:11,983
Wannable,

908
00:38:12,753 --> 00:38:15,113
I hope you remember me.

909
00:38:16,023 --> 00:38:19,323
Thank you for cheering us on back in the day.

910
00:38:19,493 --> 00:38:22,422
I'm doing well now, so please don't worry about me.

911
00:38:22,423 --> 00:38:25,493
I hope you'll always be happy.

912
00:38:26,363 --> 00:38:27,492
I love you.

913
00:38:27,493 --> 00:38:31,333
(I love you, Wannable.)

914
00:38:31,933 --> 00:38:33,603
Jin Young, say something.

915
00:38:34,633 --> 00:38:36,872
Now, the Open Pick Voting that'll determine...

916
00:38:36,873 --> 00:38:38,673
next week's opening will begin.

917
00:38:40,173 --> 00:38:41,442
Between the two following videos,

918
00:38:41,443 --> 00:38:43,683
vote for the one you want to watch the full version of.

919
00:38:44,683 --> 00:38:46,312
The video with more votes...

920
00:38:46,313 --> 00:38:48,413
will get chosen as next week's opening.

921
00:38:49,183 --> 00:38:50,782
Play the first video.

922
00:38:50,783 --> 00:38:52,463
(A: Full version of the "NEVER" challenge)

923
00:38:52,523 --> 00:38:54,152
Who wants to be the cameraman?

924
00:38:54,153 --> 00:38:55,993
We need someone to do this.

925
00:38:56,123 --> 00:38:58,192
(The "NEVER" challenge suddenly begins.)

926
00:38:58,193 --> 00:38:59,433
(Who will be the cameraman?)

927
00:38:59,533 --> 00:39:02,432
(Coach Sung can do what's trendy.)

928
00:39:02,433 --> 00:39:04,003
(He loses a shoe in the end.)

929
00:39:04,103 --> 00:39:05,262
(Laughing to death)

930
00:39:05,263 --> 00:39:07,379
(Pick A if you're curious about Coach Sung's filming!)

931
00:39:07,403 --> 00:39:09,072
(B: Full version of the "Beautiful" challenge)

932
00:39:09,073 --> 00:39:10,673
Play the second video.

933
00:39:11,143 --> 00:39:13,242
I heard that they rebanded.

934
00:39:13,243 --> 00:39:14,272
Did they?

935
00:39:14,273 --> 00:39:17,742
Gosh, they were quite popular back in 2017.

936
00:39:17,743 --> 00:39:21,453
(Even after 7 years, they remember the dance moves.)

937
00:39:21,813 --> 00:39:23,652
Ji Hoon has different vibes.

938
00:39:23,653 --> 00:39:26,333
(Pick B if you're curious about a different "Beautiful" challenge.)

939
00:39:26,753 --> 00:39:29,522
You can vote on Mnet Plus, the official platform of the show.

940
00:39:29,523 --> 00:39:31,792
Log into the page of "WANNA ONE GO: Back to Base,"

941
00:39:31,793 --> 00:39:34,263
and click on vote button for the Open Pick Voting.

942
00:39:35,463 --> 00:39:37,303
Choose 1 of the 2 candidates,

943
00:39:37,763 --> 00:39:40,032
and submit your vote.

944
00:39:40,033 --> 00:39:42,773
You'll get a Vote Certificate and the voting process will end.

945
00:39:43,473 --> 00:39:44,702
Wannable,

946
00:39:44,703 --> 00:39:47,512
please vote for the video that charmed your heart.

947
00:39:47,513 --> 00:39:49,759
(The 2nd Open Pick Voting ends at 11:59pm on May 7, 2026.)

948
00:39:49,783 --> 00:39:50,783
(Ringing)

949
00:39:50,883 --> 00:39:52,012
(The doorbell suddenly rings!)

950
00:39:52,013 --> 00:39:53,333
(They go to the door right away.)

951
00:39:53,413 --> 00:39:55,429
(Wanna Base's first puppy guests, Max and Vero are here.)

952
00:39:55,453 --> 00:39:57,699
(The director of a movie that got 16 million views, Jang Hang Jun!)

953
00:39:57,723 --> 00:40:01,593
(What happened to Wanna Base?)

954
00:40:25,013 --> 00:40:26,382
(You can check out the OST, "WE WANNA GO,")

955
00:40:26,383 --> 00:40:28,183
(at various music platforms at 6pm on May 6.)
